[[Image:Purityball.jpg|thumb|right|150px|The younger we get them, the better.]]
A '''purity ball''' is an event where [[loli]]s pledge their virginity to their fathers in the name of [[God]]. It’s most common among the [[pedophiles|Evangelical Christian]] community. The supposed aims of a Purity Ball include:

*The promotion of [[lie|sexual abstinence]] and purity before marriage.
*Reaffirming the [[incest|father-daughter]] relationship and their relationship with God.
*For fathers to take up the responsibility as [[pimp|“guardians”]] of their daughter’s purity.

==What happens at Purity Balls?==
