The main part of the evening is, of course, the pledge where the fathers pledge to be her “authority and protection in the area of purity” ([http://www.generationsoflight.com/generationsoflight/html/index.html actual pledge])

Whether this means the father gets to be the first one to pop his daughter’s cherry is open to each individual's interpretation.

